criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 4-18 years;

          -  IBS diagnosis according to Roma III criteria;

          -  Written informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Coeliac disease;

          -  Wheat allergy;

          -  Others food allergy;

          -  Type 1 Diabetes;

          -  Others Chronic and or Malignant diseases;

          -  H. Pylori infection.
